title: Premium Baby Stroller and Car Seat Combo Trend Jogging Pram Travel System Graco
text: Premium Baby Stroller and car Seat Combo Trend Jogging Pram Travel System Graco Stroller Originally Posted On: Amazon Additional Comments: Includes the Graco snugride click connect 35 infant car seat, rear facing for infants from 4-35lbs and up to 32" One-2nd, one-hand fold provides the ultimate in convenience for moms on-the-go Air-filled rubber tires offer suspension for a smooth ride on any terrain Locking front swivel wheel provides an easy transition from daily strolling to jogging. Lock the front wheel for added stability while running and unlock the wheel for maneuverability on daily strolls.
